Images: ['[630_360_15271...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2018_05/thumb_files/630_360_1527140694-3722.jpg)', '[1689263975-10...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_07/1689263975-102.jpeg)']

